OL,3,CCouncil forced to allow takeaways near
OL,4,Cprimary schools after KFC fight
OL,6,FHealth chiefs say profits are being
OL,7,Fput before children's health after KFC
OL,8,Fsuccessfully fought plans to ban
OL,9,Ftakeaways near schools.
OL,11,FCouncil is one of 24 local authorities
OL,12,Fwhich have reportedly been forced to
OL,13,Fbacktrack on efforts to prevent fast
OL,14,Ffood being sold to pupils.
OL,16,FUnder its local plan, it wanted to
OL,17,Fenforce rules which would have meant
OL,18,Fnew hot food takeaways could not open
OL,19,Fwithin 400m of both primary and
OL,20,Fsecondary schools.
