OL,6,FBut the planning inspectorate
OL,7,Fpartially upheld an appeal by KFC,
OL,8,Fmeaning the policy will only apply to
OL,9,Fsecondary schools.
OL,11,FA watered down local plan - with no
OL,12,Fexclusion zone for primary schools -
OL,13,Fwas published by Wakefield Council in
OL,14,FJanuary.
OL,16,FSteve Turnbull, interim director of
OL,17,Fpublic health at the council, said it
OL,18,Fwas a "surprise".
