OL,3,CCouncil forced to allow takeaways near
OL,4,Cprimary schools after KFC fight
OL,6,FAccording to reports, since 2017 16
OL,7,Fcouncils have abandoned plans to ban
OL,8,Ftakeaways. A further eight have had to
OL,9,Flimit the extent of their powers,
OL,10,Fafter the fast food giant responded to
OL,11,Fpublic consultations.
OL,13,FMr Turnbull said efforts to battle
OL,14,Fobesity were being compromised.
OL,16,F"(It's) unfortunate because it exposes
OL,17,Fmore children and families to ready
OL,18,Faccess to hot food takeaways on a
OL,19,Fregular basis," he said.
