OL,6,F"It can form a habit and it can make
OL,7,Fit harder and harder to live a healthy
OL,8,Flife. It is a setback, because we're
OL,9,Ftrying to create a healthy
OL,10,Fenvironment."
OL,12,FFran Bernhardt, of the food charity
OL,13,FSustain, said: "We really should be
OL,14,Fasking, 'is healthier food more
OL,15,Favailable, affordable, accessible and
OL,16,Fappealing as unhealthy food?' and, in
OL,17,Fthe vast majority of places across the
OL,18,FUK, that's simply not the case."
