OL,6,FIn a statement, KFC said it took its
OL,7,Frole in making a "positive
OL,8,Fcontribution" to communities
OL,9,F"extremely seriously".
OL,11,FIt added: "Like many businesses, we
OL,12,Ftake up opportunities to contribute
OL,13,Fwhen local authorities seek the views
OL,14,Fof relevant parties on things like
OL,15,Fplanning policy.
OL,17,F"This is a standard part of the policy
OL,18,Fmaking process to ensure potentially
OL,19,Funconsidered impacts on the local area
OL,20,Fare brought to light.
